dc_title_s: Plan and profile of Umpqua River above Scottsburg, Oregon : North Umpqua River and tributaries
dc_description_s: Relief shown by contours and spot heights.; "Surveyed in 1914 and 1924."; Topography also done by R.B. Kilgore.; Vertical scale of profiles 1 in. = 40 ft.; Sheet E includes map of Lake Creek and part of the North Umpqua River.
